IRS990.ActivityOrMissionDescription: THE ASSOCIATION OF GAMING EQUIPMENT MANUFACTURERS (AGEM) IS AN INTERNATIONAL TRADE ASSOCIATION REPRESENTING MANUFACTURERS OF ELECTRONIC GAMING DEVICES, SYSTEMS, AND COMPONENTS FOR THE GAMING INDUSTRY. THE ASSOCIATION, AS A GOOD CORPORATE CITIZEN, IDENTIFIES AND ACTS UPON ISSUES RELATING TO EDUCATION, TRADE SHOW REPRESENTATION, REGULATION, MANUFACTURING AND LICENSING STANDARDS, AND PROMOTES THE EXPANSION OF RESPONSIBLE GAMING FOR THE BENEFIT OF ITS MEMBERS AND THE INDUSTRY.
